descriptionHtml:
This mod extendeds Tel Mythrin village. Before it was empty and not very detailed. This mod will not delete any original structure, it just adds clutter like tables, crates and especially more light sources. Additonal you will find your own cozy mushroom house. 

The aim of this mod is to improve Solstheims villages and landscapes. It does not affect any gameplay mechanisms. The new house is fully nav meshed and cleaned up. No bugs or incompability cases are known. Also avaiable in Steam Workshop. 

Just look at the screenshots and give it I try, I\\\\\\\'m sure you will like it. For questions and/or hints for improvement or other wishes just write me!
